Lie with Me;;2005;;Not Rated;;Drama,Romance;;5.3;;Clement Virgo;;Lauren Lee Smith,Eric Balfour,Polly Shannon,Mayko Nguyen,Michael Facciolo,Kate Lynch,Ron White,Kristin Lehman,Don Francks,Richard Chevolleau,Frank Chiesurin,Nicola Lipman,Theresa Tova;;In Toronto, the nymphomaniac Leila spends the nights dancing and having sex with men to satisfy her sex drive. Leila learns that her parents are divorcing and she is affected by their decision. When Leila meets David, she has a torrid affair with him. David is an artist that lives with his father, who is very dependent on David. Leila and David have a complicated relationship since he is a possessive man that demands commitment but Leila does not know how to love a man and has the need of different partners in her sex life.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0418832/